@startuml seq_06_view_activity_history
title Sequence Diagram: UC-06 View Activity History

actor User
participant "User Web" as Frontend
participant "Activity Controller" as Controller
participant "Activity Service" as Service
participant "Activity Repository" as Repo

User -> Frontend: Open Activity History page
Frontend -> Controller: GET /api/users/activity-history?page=1
Controller -> Service: Get Paginated History (userID, page)
Service -> Repo: Fetch Activity Records
Repo --> Service: List of Records & Pagination Data

alt Records found
    Service --> Controller: History Data
    Controller --> Frontend: 200 OK (Data array)
    Frontend --> User: Display Activity List
else No records found
    Service --> Controller: Empty List
    Controller --> Frontend: 200 OK (Empty array)
    Frontend --> User: Display "No activity" state
end
@enduml